  "motivation": "The LayoutShift API currently reports shift rectangles in physical pixels, which is inconsistent with most other layout-related APIs that use CSS pixels. This inconsistency can be confusing for developers, especially when debugging or comparing against DevTools. This flag introduces the option to switch to CSS pixels for better developer experience and alignment.",
